{
  "name": "w06_d01_02.ks",
  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040024\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "line": "「兄さん、ごめんなさい、待たせちゃった？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "line": "「いや、さっき来たところだから、全然大丈夫だ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "line": "放課後。弥恵と待ち合わせていた昇降口に先に着いたのは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "line": "俺の方だった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "line": "とは言っても、弥恵がまだ来ていないことを確認した\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "line": "すぐあとには、遠くから小走りで駆け寄ってくる姿が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "line": "見えていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040025\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "line": "「は……はうぅぅ……息、切れちゃった……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "line": "「そんなに急がなくてもよかったのに」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040026\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "line": "「だ……だって、ホームルームが少し長引いちゃって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040027\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "line": "「兄さんを待たせちゃいけないって思って……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "line": "　ふぅ、ふぅ、ふぅ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "line": "大きく息をついて、呼吸を整えようとする。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "line": "「そっか。はは……ありがとうな、弥恵」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "line": "そんないじらしい様子に、ついつい顔が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "line": "ほころんでしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040028\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "line": "「え？　なにかそんなに面白かった……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "line": "「ううん。ただ、弥恵らしいなぁって思っただけだ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040029\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "line": "「わたし、らしい……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040030\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "line": "「ひょ、ひょっとしてそれって、ドジっていうこと……？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "line": "　うぅ、ぅぅぅ〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "line": "「どうしてそうなるんだ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "line": "「そうじゃなくて、俺のこと気遣って急いで来ようとして\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "line": "　くれるところが弥恵らしいってだけだから、安心して」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040031\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "line": "「あ……そ、そうなんだ、よかった」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "line": "「納得してくれたか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040032\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "line": "「う、うんっ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "line": "「よかった。それじゃ行こう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040033\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "line": "「……活動場所探し？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 142,
      "line": "「ああ。まずは学校で活動させてもらえる場所を確保する\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 143,
      "line": "　ことから始めるべきかなって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 149,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040034\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 150,
      "line": "「そっか……そうだよね……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 153,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 154,
      "line": "「とにかく、考えられる場所は全てあたってみよう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 160,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040035\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 161,
      "line": "「うん。ありがとう、兄さん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 164,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 165,
      "line": "俺の説明に、笑顔でうなずいてくれる弥恵。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 174,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 175,
      "line": "けど、正直なところ、この場所探しは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 176,
      "line": "良い結果を出すことが難しいと言わざるを得ない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 180,
      "line": "お菓子を作るという性質上、どうしても流し台やコンロ、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 181,
      "line": "そしてオーブン……とまではいかなくとも、電子レンジ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 182,
      "line": "くらいは必要になってしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 185,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186,
      "line": "そうなると、場所は一気に限定されてしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 189,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 190,
      "line": "そしてそういう場所は大抵、既に使われているもので。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 205,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160037\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 206,
      "line": "\t「あれ、和哉くんじゃないか。今日はどうしたのかな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 207,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33892\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 209,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210,
      "line": "\t「どうも。この前はお世話になりました、部長さん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 211,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33893\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 213,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160038\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 214,
      "line": "\t「智花ちゃんに会いに来たのかい？　今日はあいにく\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 215,
      "line": "\t　欠席なんだが」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 216,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33894\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 218,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160039\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 219,
      "line": "\t「それとも、今日こそ部活動監査なのかな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 220,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33895\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 222,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 223,
      "line": "\t「いえ、今日はまた違う用件なんですが……少しお話を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 224,
      "line": "\t　聞いてもらえませんか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 225,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33896\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160040\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 230,
      "line": "\t「はいはい。えっと……どちら様かな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 231,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33897\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 234,
      "line": "\t「あの、こちらでお世話になっています、倉野智花の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 235,
      "line": "\t　双子の弟で、倉野和哉といいます」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 236,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33898\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 238,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160041\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 239,
      "line": "\t「ああ、智花ちゃんの。姉弟がいるとは聞いていたけど、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 240,
      "line": "\t　双子なのか。確かにとてもよく似ているね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33899\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 243,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160042\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 244,
      "line": "\t「あ、確か生徒会役員なんだっけ？　ということは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 245,
      "line": "\t　部活動監査かい？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33900\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 248,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 249,
      "line": "\t「いえ、それとは違う用件なんですが……少しお話を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250,
      "line": "\t　聞いてもらえませんか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 251,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33901\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 255,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160043\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 256,
      "line": "「ああ、それは構わないけど。じゃあ、あっちでいいかな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 262,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263,
      "line": "部長さんは教室の後方にある、少し開けたスペースを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264,
      "line": "指差した。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 267,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 268,
      "line": "「はい、ありがとうございます」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 276,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040036\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 277,
      "line": "\t「兄さん、家庭科部の部長さんと知り合いなの？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 278,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33905\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 280,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 281,
      "line": "\t「ああ。智花の付き添いで一度おじゃました事があって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 282,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33906\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 284,
      "line": "\t@action id=弥恵 action=ActionAdvBow height=10 cycle=500 count=1\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 286,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040037\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 287,
      "line": "\t「そうだったんだ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 288,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33907\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 290,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160044\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 291,
      "line": "\t「それで、今日はまた可愛い子を連れているけど、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 292,
      "line": "\t　その子が和哉くんの彼女なのかな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 293,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33908\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 295,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160045\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 296,
      "line": "\t「智花ちゃんがいない隙を窺って、私に紹介しに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 297,
      "line": "\t　来てくれたとか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 298,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33909\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 300,
      "line": "\t@char file=CD03008M\t\t\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 301,
      "line": "\t@action id=弥恵 action=ActionAdvHop width=2 height=2 cycle=100 count=15\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 303,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040038\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 304,
      "line": "\t「かかかか、彼女っ！？　はわわわわっ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 305,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33910\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 307,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 308,
      "line": "\tこの前、俺も受けたからかいに、まんまと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 309,
      "line": "\t捕まってしまう弥恵。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 310,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33911\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 312,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 313,
      "line": "\t「あはは……いえ、残念ですけど。一つ下の、妹の弥恵……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 314,
      "line": "\t　倉野弥恵といいます」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 315,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33912\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 317,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 318,
      "line": "\t「弥恵。ほら、挨拶して」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 319,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33913\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 321,
      "line": "\t@char file=CD03015M\t\t\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 322,
      "line": "\t@action id=弥恵 action=ActionAdvJump height=10 cycle=300 count=1\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 324,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040039\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 325,
      "line": "\t「あっ。は、はうぅぅ……ごめんなさい、兄さん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 326,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33914\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 328,
      "line": "\t@char file=CD03014M\t\t\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 329,
      "line": "\t@action id=弥恵 action=ActionAdvBow height=10 cycle=500 count=1\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 331,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040040\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 332,
      "line": "\t「あ、あの、１年の倉野弥恵です。姉がいつもお世話に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 333,
      "line": "\t　なっておりますっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 334,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33915\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 336,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160046\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 337,
      "line": "\t「ははっ。これは、智花ちゃんとは全然違うタイプの\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 338,
      "line": "\t　妹さんだね、びっくりだよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 339,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33916\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 341,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160047\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 342,
      "line": "\t「そんなに硬くならないで。こちらこそよろしくね、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 343,
      "line": "\t　弥恵ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 344,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33917\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 346,
      "line": "\t@char file=CD03003M\t\t\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 347,
      "line": "\t@action id=弥恵 action=ActionAdvHop width=2 height=2 cycle=100 count=5\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 349,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040041\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 350,
      "line": "\t「は、はいっ。あ、ありがとうございっ、ます」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 351,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33918\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 353,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 354,
      "line": "\t全く硬さの取れない弥恵の反応に、軽く苦笑いを浮かべる\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 355,
      "line": "\t部長さん。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 356,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33919\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 358,
      "line": "\t@hide\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 359,
      "line": "\t@cg file=black\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 360,
      "line": "\t@update transition=universal rule=WIP_MOZH time=500\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 361,
      "line": "\t@waitUpdate\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 362,
      "line": "\t@cg file=BG018a pos=-320,0,0\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 363,
      "line": "\t@update transition=universal rule=WIP_MOZH time=500\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 364,
      "line": "\t@waitUpdate\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 366,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160048\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 367,
      "line": "\t「それで、また違う用件っていうのは、一体なにかな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
