    {
      "lineNumber": 380,
      "line": "\t@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160049\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 381,
      "line": "\t「それで用件っていうのは、一体なにかな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 382,
      "line": "\t@Hitret id=33921\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 386,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 387,
      "line": "「はい。それが……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 396,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160050\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 397,
      "line": "「はぁぁ……うーん……同好会ねぇ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 400,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 401,
      "line": "「……はい。検討していただけないでしょうか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 406,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040042\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 407,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 410,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 411,
      "line": "同好会の説明を終えると、難しい表情を浮かべてしまった\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 412,
      "line": "部長さん。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 415,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 416,
      "line": "その反応が、全てを物語っていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 421,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160051\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 422,
      "line": "「新しい部を作りたいって意欲に水を差したくはないけど、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 423,
      "line": "　ウチはウチで毎日活動してるしね……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 426,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160052\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 427,
      "line": "「それに、見てもらえば分かると思うけど、部員も\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 428,
      "line": "　そこそこいるんだ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 431,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160053\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 432,
      "line": "「調理実習室の一角だけ別の部が活動してるっていうのも\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 433,
      "line": "　おかしな話になっちゃうし……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 436,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 437,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 440,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160054\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 441,
      "line": "「えっと、弥恵ちゃん……だったよね？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 442,
      "line": "　あなたが同好会の発案者ってことでいいのかな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 448,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040043\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 449,
      "line": "「ぁ……えと……はい……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 452,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160055\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 453,
      "line": "「同好会じゃなきゃダメなのかな？　智花ちゃんと一緒に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 454,
      "line": "　家庭科部に入ってもらえたら、私としては嬉しいん\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 455,
      "line": "　だけどな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 461,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040044\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 462,
      "line": "「え？　あ、あ、あの、それは……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 465,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160056\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 466,
      "line": "「確かにウチはお菓子だけを作っているわけじゃないけど、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 467,
      "line": "　作ることだってもちろんあるし、他の知識を身に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 468,
      "line": "　つけるのも悪くないと思うよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 474,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040045\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 475,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 478,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 479,
      "line": "部長さんの言葉に弥恵はしゅん、としてしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 482,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 483,
      "line": "まるで、昨日の生徒会室でのやりとりの繰り返しみたいに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 484,
      "line": "なってしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 489,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160057\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 490,
      "line": "「……ごめんなさい。偉そうなことを言っちゃったね。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 491,
      "line": "　今のは忘れて？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 494,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 495,
      "line": "「いえ。こちらこそ、無理なお願いをして\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 496,
      "line": "　すみませんでした」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 499,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 500,
      "line": "「じゃあ、俺たちはこれで……行こう、弥恵」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 506,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040046\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 507,
      "line": "「ぁ……う、うん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 513,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040047\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 514,
      "line": "「あ、あの。お話しを聞いていただいて、ありがとう\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 515,
      "line": "　ございました」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 518,
      "line": "@Talk name=家庭科部部長 voice=NP160058\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 519,
      "line": "「うん。力になってあげられなくてごめんね。弥恵ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 522,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 523,
      "line": "「失礼しました」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 533,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 534,
      "line": "「……ふぅ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 537,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 538,
      "line": "廊下に出て、ため息をひとつ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 541,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 542,
      "line": "難しい結果を前にして、どうしても気持ちが沈んでしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 548,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040048\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 549,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 552,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 553,
      "line": "そんな俺の横で、力なくうなだれてしまった弥恵。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 558,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 559,
      "line": "「そんな顔しないで。まだ１件回っただけだろ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 565,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040049\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 566,
      "line": "「ぁ。兄さん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 569,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 570,
      "line": "すっかり元気を無くしてしまった頭を、やんわりと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 571,
      "line": "さするようになでた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 577,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040050\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 578,
      "line": "「……うん、そうだよね。これからだよね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 581,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 582,
      "line": "やせ我慢かもしれないけど、弥恵は微笑みを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 583,
      "line": "取り戻してくれる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 586,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 587,
      "line": "「じゃあ、次のところに行ってみようか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 593,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040051\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 594,
      "line": "「うん。そうする」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 597,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 598,
      "line": "少しだけ元気を取り戻してくれた弥恵を連れて、次の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 599,
      "line": "活動場所候補へ向かった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 607,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 608,
      "line": "だが、調理実習室以外で料理が可能な部屋が一般的な\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 609,
      "line": "公立校にあるわけはなく。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 612,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 613,
      "line": "残る選択肢は、電子レンジが置かれている教員室。そして\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 614,
      "line": "コンロが設置されている理科室……その程度だった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 626,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 627,
      "line": "当然のように結果は思わしくなくて。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 630,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 631,
      "line": "「あとは……どこかないかなぁ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 634,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 635,
      "line": "校舎の端から端まで、全ての教室の可能性を順に考えて\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 636,
      "line": "いくものの、望んだ結論には至らない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 642,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040052\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 643,
      "line": "「兄さん。今日はこのくらいにして、もう帰ろう？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 644,
      "line": "　お店も気になるし……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 647,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 648,
      "line": "「え？　ああ。確かにだいぶ時間も\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 649,
      "line": "　経っちゃってるけど……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 655,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 656,
      "line": "気がつけば日はかなり西に傾いていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 659,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 660,
      "line": "今日は生徒会も休みだったからいずみ姉さんも店に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 661,
      "line": "居てくれているはずだし、問題はなさそうに感じるけど。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 664,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 665,
      "line": "パティシエとして店を支えてきたことで、元々強い\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 666,
      "line": "責任感がいっそう強いものになっているのかもしれない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 673,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040053\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 674,
      "line": "「ごめんね。わたしたち、兄さんを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 675,
      "line": "　困らせちゃってるよね……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 678,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 679,
      "line": "「困らせるだなんて、そんな風に思ってなんかないよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 682,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 683,
      "line": "「弥恵と絵麻に協力したくてこうしているだけなんだから、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 684,
      "line": "　気にするなって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 690,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040054\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 691,
      "line": "「うん……ごめんなさい……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 705,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040055\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 706,
      "line": "「え？　兄さん、あれ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 709,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 710,
      "line": "弥恵の言葉を聞き入れて、家へと帰った俺たち。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 713,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 714,
      "line": "そこにあったのは、意外な光景だった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 720,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040056\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 721,
      "line": "「お店が閉まってる……どうして……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 731,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM040001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 732,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん、お姉ちゃん、おかえりなさいです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 737,
      "line": "@Talk name=みこと voice=MK040001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 738,
      "line": "「あ。カズくんっ、やえもおかえりーーーっ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 741,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 742,
      "line": "「みこと姉ちゃん、なんで店が——」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 747,
      "line": "@Talk name=みこと voice=MK040002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 748,
      "line": "「うん。今日は開けてからず〜っと忙しかったんだけど、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 749,
      "line": "　商品が売りきれちゃったんだよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 756,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM040002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 757,
      "line": "「青天の霹靂、です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 763,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 764,
      "line": "絵麻の言葉通りの光景が、店内には広がっていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 767,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 768,
      "line": "ショーケースはもちろん、戸棚やバスケットに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 769,
      "line": "飾るように配置されていた焼き菓子までが、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 770,
      "line": "ひとつ残らず無くなっている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 777,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040057\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 778,
      "line": "「……っ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 783,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 784,
      "line": "「そうだったのか……手伝えなくてごめん、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 785,
      "line": "　みこと姉ちゃん。絵麻も、ごめんな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 791,
      "line": "@Talk name=みこと voice=MK040003\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 792,
      "line": "「カズくんが謝ることなんていっこもないよっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 798,
      "line": "@Talk name=みこと voice=MK040004\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 799,
      "line": "「お客さんが急にたくさん来ることなんて、昔から\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 800,
      "line": "　しょっちゅうだったじゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 806,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM040003\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 807,
      "line": "「はい。しょっちゅうです。洋菓子店あるあるです」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 814,
      "line": "@Talk name=無音/絵麻\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 815,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 820,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM040004\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 821,
      "line": "「……お姉ちゃん？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 828,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040058\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 829,
      "line": "「ぇ？　あ、うんっ。なにかな、絵麻ちゃん？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 835,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM040005\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 836,
      "line": "「お姉ちゃん、お顔の色がすぐれません。おからだの調子\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 837,
      "line": "　悪いです？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 843,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040059\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 844,
      "line": "「ううん、そんなことないよ、全然平気っ。平気だから」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 851,
      "line": "@Talk name=みこと voice=MK040005\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 852,
      "line": "「ん〜、でもえまの言うとおりだよ？　顔色よくないし、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 853,
      "line": "　部屋で休んでおいで？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 859,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040060\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 860,
      "line": "「でっ、でも、ダメだよ、お片付け手伝わなくちゃ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 866,
      "line": "@Talk name=みこと voice=MK040006\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 867,
      "line": "「だぁ〜めーだーよー！　お姉ちゃんの言うことは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 868,
      "line": "　聞かなくちゃだーめーっ！！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 874,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM040006\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 875,
      "line": "「妹の言うことも、聞く義務があります」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 880,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040061\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 881,
      "line": "「……でも……だって……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 886,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 887,
      "line": "「弥恵、二人の言うとおりだよ、部屋に戻って休もう？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 893,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040062\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 894,
      "line": "「兄さん、でも……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 899,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 900,
      "line": "弥恵はなんだか泣いてしまいそうなくらい弱々しい表情に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 901,
      "line": "なっていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 904,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 905,
      "line": "弥恵はきっと、責任を感じているんだろう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 908,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 909,
      "line": "今日の朝、もっと仕込みの量を増やしていれば。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 912,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 913,
      "line": "放課後、同好会のことなんて考えずにまっすぐ家に帰って\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 914,
      "line": "いれば。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 917,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 918,
      "line": "そんな風に。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 925,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040063\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 926,
      "line": "「……うん。わかった……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 929,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 930,
      "line": "「じゃあ、いずみ姉さんと智花に挨拶して、部屋に戻ろう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 935,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 936,
      "line": "「ちょっと弥恵に付き添ってくるよ、すぐに戻るから」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 942,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM040007\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 943,
      "line": "「はい。お姉ちゃんのことよろしくです。お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 949,
      "line": "@Talk name=みこと voice=MK040007\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 950,
      "line": "「やえ、またあとでね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 956,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040064\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 957,
      "line": "「うん。みこと姉さん、絵麻ちゃん、ごめんね……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 969,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM040001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 970,
      "line": "「あ、和哉。弥恵も、おかえりなさい」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 976,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS040001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 977,
      "line": "「おかえりなさい、ふたりとも」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 983,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS040002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 984,
      "line": "「ふふ。みことちゃんが騒いでいたから、すぐに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 985,
      "line": "　分かったわ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 990,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 991,
      "line": "洗い終えたティーカップやスプーンを丁寧に拭いていた\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 992,
      "line": "いずみ姉さんと智花。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 995,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 996,
      "line": "「うん、ただいま。ごめん二人とも、手伝えなくて」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1002,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS040003\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1003,
      "line": "「気にすることないわ。ルール通りにお店を開けただけ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1004,
      "line": "　ですもの」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1010,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM040002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1011,
      "line": "「ごめんね、弥恵。私がもっと力になれたら、店閉めたり\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1012,
      "line": "　せずにすんだんだけど……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1018,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040065\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1019,
      "line": "「ぁ、あの……えとっ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1024,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS040004\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1025,
      "line": "「あら。弥恵ちゃん、顔色がよくないわね？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1031,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM040003\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1032,
      "line": "「あ……本当だ……調子悪いの？　無理しちゃダメ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1033,
      "line": "　じゃない」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1039,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM040004\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1040,
      "line": "「とりあえず横になろう？　こっちのことは私たちに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1041,
      "line": "　任せてくれればいいから」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1049,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS040005\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1050,
      "line": "「ふふ。智花ちゃんったら、頼もしいわね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1056,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM040005\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1057,
      "line": "「ちょ……な、なによ、いずみ姉。からかわないでっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1063,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS040006\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1064,
      "line": "「ふふふっ、ごめんなさい、智花ちゃんもお姉さん\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1065,
      "line": "　なんだなぁって思ったら嬉しくなっちゃってつい、ね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1072,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM040006\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1073,
      "line": "「っ、も、もぉぉ〜！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1080,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS040007\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1081,
      "line": "「弥恵ちゃん、日頃の疲れが溜まっているのかも\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1082,
      "line": "　しれないわ。今はゆっくり休んでね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1087,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS040008\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1088,
      "line": "「元気になったら、また頑張りましょう？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1094,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040066\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1095,
      "line": "「……っ……う、うん……分かった……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1098,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1099,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1111,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1112,
      "line": "弥恵に付き添って、部屋の前までやってくる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1115,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1116,
      "line": "その間、弥恵は言葉を発しなかった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1121,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040067\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1122,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1125,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1126,
      "line": "「水かなにか、持ってこようか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1132,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040068\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1133,
      "line": "「ううん、大丈夫だから……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1136,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1137,
      "line": "沈んだ面持ちでうつむいて、小さく縮こまってしまって。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1142,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040069\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1143,
      "line": "「それじゃあわたし、ちょっと横になるから」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1149,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040070\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1150,
      "line": "「みんなのお手伝い、お願いしちゃうね、兄さん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1156,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040071\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1157,
      "line": "「じゃあ、またあとで——」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1160,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1161,
      "line": "「弥恵」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1166,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1167,
      "line": "そんな姿、見ていられなかった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1174,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040072\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1175,
      "line": "「？　ぇ……兄さん……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1178,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1179,
      "line": "やんわりと、包み込むように。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1185,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1186,
      "line": "さらさらの髪の毛を優しく梳くようにして、頭をなでる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1191,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1192,
      "line": "気持ちを落としてしまった今の弥恵には、なにを言っても\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1193,
      "line": "重荷になるだけのような気がして。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1196,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1197,
      "line": "だから、ただ、分かってほしかった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1200,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1201,
      "line": "誰よりもアップルパイのために尽くしてくれている弥恵が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1202,
      "line": "必要以上に責任を感じる事なんてないんだって。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1205,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1206,
      "line": "ひとりで背負い込もうとする必要なんてないんだって。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1211,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040073\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1212,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1218,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE040074\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1219,
      "line": "「……ありがとう……兄さん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1222,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1223,
      "line": "「ん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1229,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1230,
      "line": "ゆっくりと、弥恵は俺の肩口に頭をあずけてくる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1233,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1234,
      "line": "そのまましばらくの間、俺たちはなにを言うこともなく、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 1235,
      "line": "そうしていた。\r\n"
    }
  ]
}